      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i'm studying for my accounting exam and im stuck on depreciation. can u show me the formula for straight-line depreciation and do an example? lets say i have some heavy machinery that cost 50000, its got a salvage value of 5000 and a useful life of 5 years. thanks",
